snippet.title: Eastfound Teaser (2018)
snippet.description:
Eastfound will come out in late 2018 for STEAM, PS4 and maybe Nintendo Switch and iOS & Android.

Action Adventure at its best! Fight enemies with a wide arsenal of different weapons, solve puzzles, follow the story and explore the huge world of Auri!
